releaseNotes: Sorry for two updates in two days but I have to do it to contrast piracy;
Remember to open the app for the first time you update and then re-apply the icon pack to the launcher;
Do this expecially if you are using OnePlus Launcher;
I've improved the UI too, adding Material 2 cards style;
If you face problems with Lawnchair, they depends by the launcher caused by the switch from v1 to v2;
Thanks for choose Pixelful, have a nice day.
